Title: Provides that information on a sex offender from another state who has not been assigned a risk level in this state, may be disclosed as if he or she was a level 2 sex offender
Summary: Provides that information on a sex offender from another state who has not been assigned a risk level in this state, may be disclosed as if he or she was a level 2 sex offender.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the correction law, in relation to dissemination of information on sex offenders from another state who have not been assigned a risk level in this state
